BlackBox.name: Clash.Signal.BiSignal.veryUnsafeToBiSignalIn
BlackBox.type:
veryUnsafeToBiSignalIn :: ( HasCallStack        -- ARG[0]
                                         , Show a              -- ARG[1]
                                         , KnownNat m          -- ARG[2]
                                         , m ~ BitSize a       -- ARG[3]
                                         , BitPack a           -- ARG[4]
                                         , Typeable a          -- ARG[5]
                                         , Typeable ds         -- ARG[6]
                                         , Typeable d          -- ARG[7]
                                         )
                                      => BiSignalOut n ds d a  -- ARG[8]
                                      -> BiSignalIn n ds d a   -- RESULT

BlackBox.name: Clash.Signal.BiSignal.mergeBiSignalOuts
BlackBox.type:
mergeBiSignalOuts :: ( HasCallStack    -- ARG[0]
                                   , Show a          -- ARG[1]
                                   , KnownNat n      -- ARG[2]
                                   )
              => Vec n (BiSignalOut name defaultState dom a) -- ARG[3]
              -> BiSignalOut name defaultState dom a
